Package jcckit.graphic

Interface GraphicalCompositeRenderer

All Superinterfaces:
Renderer
All Known Implementing Classes:
Graphics2DRenderer
public interface GraphicalCompositeRenderer extends Renderer
Interface of all Renderers who render a GraphicalComposite. Note, that a GraphicalCompositeRenderer does not render the element of a GraphicalComposite
